init_text: You're Barack Obama. 4 years into your retirement, you awake to find a letter with no return address on your bedside table. It reads "I hope you've had a chance to relax Barack...but pack your bags and call the number below. It's time to start the real job." Signed simply, "JFK."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: JFK tells you that he has a job for you and that you will be paid handsomely.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells you to pack your bags and that you will be picked up in a few hours.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You sit in the car and the man driving tells you that you will be working with JFK.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You ask him what the job is and he tells you that you will be working with JFK to help him take down the Illuminati.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells you that they are a group of people who control the world and have been doing so for centuries.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: They are a group of people who control the world's money supply and are very rich.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He tells you that he wants to take them down and that he needs your help.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: JFK tells you that he has a plan and that he will explain it to you on the way.
